videos.description: Devin Bush's hit on Florida's Tyrie Cleveland goes under review for targeting, Bush is able to stay in the game.
videos.headline: Michigan's Bush called for late hit

videos.description: Florida's Feleipe Franks connects with Josh Hammond for the 34-yard reception.
videos.headline: Gators take a bite into Wolverine's defense

videos.description: Florida's Eddy Pineiro makes the 46-yard field goal.
videos.headline: Florida gets on the board with FG

videos.description: Michigan's Wilton Speight uses his legs to convert on third down for the Wolverines.
videos.headline: Speight keeps Michigan's drive alive

videos.description: Michigan's Ty Isaac converts on 3rd down with a 36-yard run.
videos.headline: Michigan converts another 3rd down

videos.description: Michigan's Khalid Hill gets penalized with an ineligible receiver call which takes away a touchdown for the Wolverines.
videos.headline: Michigan TD called back on ineligible receiver

videos.description: Michigan's Chris Evans eludes defenders for the 29-yard run.
videos.headline: Michigan's Evans shakes defenders for run

videos.description: Michigan's Wilton Speight finds Tarik Black for the 46-yard reception to give the Wolverines a 10-3 lead over the Gators.
videos.headline: Michigan goes long for TD

videos.description: Florida's Feleipe Franks runs for 16 yards to convert on third down for Florida.
videos.headline: Franks keeps the drive alive for the Gators

videos.description: Florida's Duke Dawson makes the interception off of the tipped pass and returns it for the touchdown.
videos.headline: Speight's misfire leads to Florida pick-six

videos.description: Michigan's Wilton Speight throws back-to-back interceptions that are returned for touchdowns as Florida takes a 17-10 lead.
videos.headline: Speight continues to struggle with second pick-six

videos.description: Florida blocks Michigan's punt to set up the offense with good field position in the first half.
videos.headline: Florida's defense continues to shine

videos.description: Michigan's John O'Korn, who is playing for the struggling Wilton Speight, finds Tarik Black for the 37-yard reception.
videos.headline: O'Korn steps up for Michigan

videos.description: Michigan's Quinn Nordin just barely makes the 55-yard field goal to bring Michigan within one score.
videos.headline: Michigan squeaks 55-yard FG through the uprights

videos.description: Florida head coach Jim McElwain discusses creating more time for QB Feleipe Franks in the game against Michigan.
videos.headline: Jim McElwain talks about making Franks more comfortable

videos.description: The first half of Florida-Michigan was dominated by big plays, mostly by the Gators defense.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Florida's defense makes big plays in 1st half) 2017/09/02

videos.headline: Florida's defense makes big plays in 1st half

videos.description: Michigan's Karan Higdon dances into the end zone to jump start the Wolverine's offense in the second half.
videos.headline: Michigan starts third quarter with TD

videos.description: After scoring a touchdown, Michigan's special teams forces a fumble on the ensuing kickoff.
videos.headline: Michigan's special teams forces fumble

videos.description: Florida's Feleipe Franks fumbles the ball and Michigan's Mich Lawrence Marshall recovers it for the Wolverines.
videos.headline: Michigan's defense stifles Florida

videos.description: Florida's Tyrie Cleveland leaps and makes the catch while falling backwards to give Florida the first down.
videos.headline: Florida's Cleveland soars to make the catch

videos.description: Michigan's Wilton Speight throws the deep ball to Nick Eubanks for 48 yards.
videos.headline: Speight airs it deep to set up Michigan

videos.description: Michigan's Noah Furbush recovers the fumble in the end zone, giving Michigan a 33-17 lead over Florida.
videos.headline: Michigan seals game with fumble recovery in end zone

videos.description: Michigan's Wilton Speight discusses the improvements he had to make between halves as Michigan takes down Florida 33-17.
videos.headline: Speight talks about recovering after a poor first half

videos.description: Todd Blackledge and Joe Tessitore break down Michigan's change between halves in their victory over Florida.
videos.headline: Looking at Michigan's impressive turnaround against Florida

videos.description: Down 17-13 after the first half, the Wolverines hold the Gators scoreless in the second half en route to a 33-17 victory.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Michigan's defense fuels second-half surge) 2017/9/2 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Michigan's defense fuels second-half surge

videos.description: After Wilton Speight throws two pick-sixes in the first half, the Wolverines dominate defensively for a second-half shutout with three takeaways.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Highlight (Michigan's defense lifts Speight in comeback win) 2017/9/3 ESHEET ENHL

videos.headline: Michigan's defense lifts Speight in comeback win
